  "detailed_description": "This is a frog jumping game<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe little frog has poor eyesight and leads the little frog to jump from one leaf to another, which will give you time.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTime is wealth, you can use your accumulated time as your own wealth, or you can contribute unselfishly.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe time contributed by all players will be aggregated into a total time in real time.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis total time will pass with the real world time.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhen this total time is 0, the game world will be reset.",
  "about_the_game": "This is a frog jumping game<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe little frog has poor eyesight and leads the little frog to jump from one leaf to another, which will give you time.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTime is wealth, you can use your accumulated time as your own wealth, or you can contribute unselfishly.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe time contributed by all players will be aggregated into a total time in real time.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis total time will pass with the real world time.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhen this total time is 0, the game world will be reset.",
